{"tid":59344,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲屋企單親 好唔相信另一半","createTime":"2016-12-29T14:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T18:49:51.000Z","uid":25733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"341c30d468535ac3c855bf0cfab2c5806b4e505c","tid":59344,"uid":25733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:40:32.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老豆以前成日偷食，後尾仲同其中一個女人生左bb<br />\n都係老母湊大我<br />\n<br />\n細個都唔覺有乜影響<br />\n大個先慢慢覺得自己好難相信另一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日想痴住男朋友，想知佢做緊乜<br />\n每廿分鐘就會想whatsapp 佢<br />\n可能只係打個emoji 話下掛住佢咁<br />\n<br />\n唔知佢幾時頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都好唔鐘意咁樣嘅自己<br />\n有冇巴絲都係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e46196cf162ae6e5a19660574171ba0334c9b0f7","tid":59344,"uid":63258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:41:33.000Z","msg":"應該同單親冇關<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此乃電腦回覆"},{"pid":"82b0929f82f3624ad9033d40a58fe2427508afc4","tid":59344,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:42:16.000Z","msg":"唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398b025009e133f4725d660edd0d88db5587fb99","tid":59344,"uid":56508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:50:22.000Z","msg":"我係覺得無永恆既愛情 <br />\n同好撚憎人偷食"},{"pid":"0e24f63b81de276db57cee6fd20af84e5a5fb540","tid":59344,"uid":25733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:54:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以前都係咁覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但每次佢一講起未來點點點<br />\n<br />\n我都會答 <br />\n<br />\n捱到嗰時先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時你偷食唔好俾我知呀  我唔知就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c2aaa25b5aea28f71038133a50d2c643e292219","tid":59344,"uid":25733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:58:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係覺得無永恆既愛情 <br />\n同好撚憎人偷食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好撚憎<br />\n<br />\n我老豆係蝗國做野，屌好撚多女<br />\n我仲親眼見過佢叫小姐<br />\n但細個唔識野<br />\n大個諗起先嘔心<br />\n<br />\n老母同爺爺投訴，當然係冇人信佢<br />\n<br />\n直至前幾年佢娶左個秘書，生左個女<br />\n我就覺得好撚頹<br />\n個女人仲要由我幼稚園睇到我大<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到我都對人冇乜信心"},{"pid":"6821ef55d9007a5dc3fa484d378ab93043bb3927","tid":59344,"uid":63127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:07:15.000Z","msg":"男朋友係單親，但父母都冇跟<br />\n之前講過d 類似結婚黎做咩？第日你同我分身家點算<br />\n(明明佢唔有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n我媽咪本身都提醒我咪同d 單親既一齊，會成日唔信人<br />\n<br />\n所以我已經好錫佢，但冇辦法做埋家庭個部分架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  見步行步算"},{"pid":"331865782c4f080ccee85b8227db6b02bd144145","tid":59344,"uid":25733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:47:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男朋友係單親，但父母都冇跟<br />\n之前講過d 類似結婚黎做咩？第日你同我分身家點算<br />\n(明明佢唔有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n我媽咪本身都提醒我咪同d 單親既一齊，會成日唔信人<br />\n<br />\n所以我已經好錫佢，但冇辦法做埋家庭個部分架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  見步行步算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢應該係無心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有時候同男朋友都會講哩啲<br />\n不過個心係好唔希望哩啲事再發生"},{"pid":"ba503bfbdea12522ba8976a3c68441ece2f7b1df","tid":59344,"uid":56508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T16:24:31.000Z","msg":"其實我都唔知自己叫信唔人信人 <br />\n我淨係覺得不論男人又好 女人又好 都會有變心既一刻<br />\n結婚都可以離婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我成日都會同自己講同另一半一齊呢一刻開心就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我又成日會諗唔好咁鍾意對方 廢事自己泥足深陷既時候佢離開我 我會好撚傷心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就好似現家咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d535be41578d8aa386270f629696451f955c95","tid":59344,"uid":235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T16:28:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e287e2ad27de457ebc2358e7e231762d31beebfc","tid":59344,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T16:30:57.000Z","msg":"不如試下改變個角度 當年你呀媽點解迫到你老豆偷食<br />\n再諗下而加你迫到條條咩地步"},{"pid":"5fe389dbc25e175017d9b7c26f0cbcd5b7e078ba","tid":59344,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T16:50:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我都唔知自己叫信唔人信人 <br />\n我淨係覺得不論男人又好 女人又好 都會有變心既一刻<br />\n結婚都可以離婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我成日都會同自己講同另一半一齊呢一刻開心就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我又成日會諗唔好咁鍾意對方 廢事自己泥足深陷既時候佢離開我 我會好撚傷心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就好似現家咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同 成日覺得唔好陷入去 雖然最後都陷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望住屋企 只能說真係哪裡有人一生只得一個女人<br />\n信唔到...愈愛就愈不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21397d055f57dd8ab3bf5e7031b663931e406ec6","tid":59344,"uid":25733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:46:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我都唔知自己叫信唔人信人 <br />\n我淨係覺得不論男人又好 女人又好 都會有變心既一刻<br />\n結婚都可以離婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我成日都會同自己講同另一半一齊呢一刻開心就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我又成日會諗唔好咁鍾意對方 廢事自己泥足深陷既時候佢離開我 我會好撚傷心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就好似現家咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然好想有長遠發展，但又好怕太鐘意嘅時候一野收皮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e9c41946b3526858fc290e41424ed83a52a8cd8","tid":59344,"uid":25733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:46:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵下自己與趣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩搵多左幾份part time <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea2d3429706506c47efcd64aa1164157fafcf54","tid":59344,"uid":70589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:49:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵下自己與趣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩搵多左幾份part time <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁姐係一日24小時係咁做?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1425e8131d6f539200e98e8ca1ea7849a43e483c","tid":59344,"uid":25733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如試下改變個角度 當年你呀媽點解迫到你老豆偷食<br />\n再諗下而加你迫到條條咩地步</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我老豆偷食，並唔係因為媽咪<br />\n唔係所有人偷食都係迫出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我爸係蝗國開工廠，一星期可能番香港一日<br />\n蝗女人貪錢唔再講<br />\n<br />\n媽咪由我好細個開始都只係每日打一次幾分鐘俾佢<br />\n嗰陣更加唔興SMS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反我男朋友老母睇到佢爸好緊<br />\n連秘書都要請個男人<br />\n去邊開會都跟住<br />\n<br />\n有時候我會諗 其實個平衡點係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔想成為佢地"},{"pid":"0e0d20a18275cc78d76f360ec961e9fbbe41684e","tid":59344,"uid":38934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:52:49.000Z","msg":"病嬌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c136e8e19696bdd258891acefbbe4c073dda271d","tid":59344,"uid":25733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:52:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搵下自己與趣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩搵多左幾份part time <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁姐係一日24小時係咁做?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇咁誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我教補習 唔係日日有堂"},{"pid":"894ff06ce37d9da92394fb0471e6f565cc6fd375","tid":59344,"uid":70589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:59:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不如試下改變個角度 當年你呀媽點解迫到你老豆偷食<br />\n再諗下而加你迫到條條咩地步</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我老豆偷食，並唔係因為媽咪<br />\n唔係所有人偷食都係迫出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我爸係蝗國開工廠，一星期可能番香港一日<br />\n蝗女人貪錢唔再講<br />\n<br />\n媽咪由我好細個開始都只係每日打一次幾分鐘俾佢<br />\n嗰陣更加唔興SMS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反我男朋友老母睇到佢爸好緊<br />\n連秘書都要請個男人<br />\n去邊開會都跟住<br />\n<br />\n有時候我會諗 其實個平衡點係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔想成為佢地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得好難搵到一個平衡點,因為始終女人心入面都會怕自己個男人去偷食<br />\n<br />\n尤其係當你年紀開始大或者一起咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你就會想做嘢去睇住個男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔經唔覺就會越做越嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de25439bec56adf1e1880e72a2664749fc1c8b10","tid":59344,"uid":46018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T18:01:22.000Z","msg":"我屋企唔係單親<br />\n但而家爸爸媽媽成日鬧交,又話後悔結婚<br />\n我都覺得佢地成日鬧交好撚煩，搞到我覺得婚姻好虛偽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10797fa32783954672a913652ace46cd65ccb058","tid":59344,"uid":70589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T18:07:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屋企唔係單親<br />\n但而家爸爸媽媽成日鬧交,又話後悔結婚<br />\n我都覺得佢地成日鬧交好撚煩，搞到我覺得婚姻好虛偽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b912b6ec7664ae49ef62a332aeabb7a0e66a590","tid":59344,"uid":25733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T18:08:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不如試下改變個角度 當年你呀媽點解迫到你老豆偷食<br />\n再諗下而加你迫到條條咩地步</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我老豆偷食，並唔係因為媽咪<br />\n唔係所有人偷食都係迫出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我爸係蝗國開工廠，一星期可能番香港一日<br />\n蝗女人貪錢唔再講<br />\n<br />\n媽咪由我好細個開始都只係每日打一次幾分鐘俾佢<br />\n嗰陣更加唔興SMS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反我男朋友老母睇到佢爸好緊<br />\n連秘書都要請個男人<br />\n去邊開會都跟住<br />\n<br />\n有時候我會諗 其實個平衡點係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔想成為佢地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得好難搵到一個平衡點,因為始終女人心入面都會怕自己個男人去偷食<br />\n<br />\n尤其係當你年紀開始大或者一起咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你就會想做嘢去睇住個男人<img src=\"